<h1 style="text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: 14.4pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 8.2pt 0cm 5.45pt 0cm;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; color: black; letter-spacing: .55pt; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;" lang="EN-US">·<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><img style="color: #333333; font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.3em;" src="/images/show/%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E7%94%A8.jpg" alt="註冊用.jpg" width="192" height="96" /></h1>
<h1 style="text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: 14.4pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 8.2pt 0cm 5.45pt 0cm;">&nbsp;</h1>
<h1 style="text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: 14.4pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 8.2pt 0cm 5.45pt 0cm;"><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; color: black; letter-spacing: .55pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size: 14pt;">榮憶橡膠工業股份有限公司</span></span></h1>
<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><a name="info01">&nbsp;</a><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司介紹</span></strong></span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 10.9pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">產業類別：</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 36.0pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">橡膠製品製造業</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">產業描述：</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 36.0pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif; font-size: 10pt;">橡膠製品製造業</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">員　　工：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">150</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">人</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">資</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">本</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">額：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">1000</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">萬元</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 35.45pt; line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">聯</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">絡</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">人：</span><span style="line-height: 10.65pt; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">郭小姐</span></span></p>
