<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a name="info02">&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">公司簡介</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">本公司成立於</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">1985</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">年，主要從事橡膠零件設計及各種工業用橡膠產品製造，擁有為數不少的客戶群，市場分佈於國內與海外。</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">我們擁有優秀的經營團隊，整體的營運穩定，獲利狀況也逐年提升。</span><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US"><br /> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">～歡迎優秀的您一起加入～</span></span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a name="info03">&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">主要商品／服務項目</span></strong></span></h2>
<p style="line-height: 10.65pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 6.55pt .0001pt 10.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">橡膠零件設計及專業製造，含</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">O</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt;">環、墊片、襯套、減震橡膠、防塵套及所有密封件</span></span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 14.4pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 16.35pt 0cm .0001pt 2.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><a name="info04">&nbsp;</a><strong><span style="color: #e57102; letter-spacing: 0.55pt; font-family: 新細明體, serif;">福利制度</span></strong></span></h2>
